at feel right? And a related question — **should the existing single-branch trail fields (`Branch`, `Base`) migrate into this new structure**, or do you want to keep backward compatibility where a trail with one branch still looks like today's format?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":681,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":34346,\"output_tokens\":604,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":681,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYniMkrZMUJ9uZyoJ5153\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"5641d712-73a4-4b8e-9b8e-6a39ab4e6bf8\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T23:43:33.339Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"5641d712-73a4-4b8e-9b8e-6a39ab4e6bf8\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/1\",\"sessionId\":\"cc5ed6bd-0c2c-4c91-94f7-7c18e3bda941\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"alex/trails-multi-pr\",\"slug\":\"jazzy-inventing-fern\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks claude-code stop\"},\"parentToolUseID\":\"ca9ce303-74db-45da-bf4d-d010eaae7c51\",\"toolUseID\":\"ca9ce303-74db-45da-bf4d-d010eaae7c51\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T23:43:33.348Z\",\"uuid\":\"16b1c207-2baa-49a0-aab7-bcdaf5e0db5a\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"16b1c207-2baa-49a0-aab7-bcdaf5e0db5a\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/1\",\"sessionId\":\"cc5ed6bd-0c2c-4c91-94f7-7c18e3bda941\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"alex/trails-multi-pr\",\"slug\":\"jazzy-inventing-fern\",\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"stop_hook_summary\",\"hookCount\":1,\"hookInfos\":[{\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd