pace/cli/.worktrees/1\",\"sessionId\":\"cc5ed6bd-0c2c-4c91-94f7-7c18e3bda941\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"alex/trails-multi-pr\",\"slug\":\"jazzy-inventing-fern\",\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"ok\"},\"uuid\":\"4f180ecc-fae9-436c-9913-68fe8fb88bb5\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-07T00:08:51.533Z\",\"permissionMode\":\"default\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"4f180ecc-fae9-436c-9913-68fe8fb88bb5\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/1\",\"sessionId\":\"cc5ed6bd-0c2c-4c91-94f7-7c18e3bda941\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"alex/trails-multi-pr\",\"slug\":\"jazzy-inventing-fern\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_019YkDWfSaraEV9MJDRnA3o3\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user wants me to present the design. Let me organize it into sections and present them one at a time, getting approval after each section.\\n\\nLet me think about the full design:\\n\\n1. **Data Model** - The new TrailMetadata with Branches, BranchEntry, PRRef types\\n2. **Storage** - How it maps to the git tree on `entire/trails/v1`\\n3. **Migration** - How existing single-branch trails upgrade\\n4. **CAS Protection** - The CheckAndSetReference retry loop\\n5. **CLI Commands** - `entire trail branch add/set-pr/list` etc.\\n6. **Hook Integration** - How post-commit finds the right trail + branch entry\\n\\n\\n7. **Lookup** - FindByBranch scanning to locate trails by branch name\\n\\nLet me start with the data model section.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":331,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":47448,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":331},\"output_tokens\":8,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYnkJvKE3oxBptxue3geh\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"f4873caa-f68b-4874-a946-2a57e81bdf9c\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-07T00:08:58.195Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"f4873caa-f68b-4874-a946-2a57e81bdf9c\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/1\",\"sessionId\":\"cc5ed6bd-0c2c-4c91-94f7-7c18e3bda941\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"alex/trails-multi-pr\",\"slug\":\"jazzy-inventing-fern\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_019YkDWfSaraEV9MJDRnA3o3\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"## Section 1: Data Model\\n\\n### Trail Metadata (revised)\\n\\n```go\\ntype Metadata struct {\\n    TrailID   ID        `json:\\\"trail_id\\\"`\\n    Title     string    `json:\\\"title\\\"`\\n    Body      string    `json:\\\"body\\\"`\\n    Status    Status    `json:\\\"status\\\"`\\n    Type      Type      `json:\\\"type,omitempty\\\"`\\n    Priority  Priority  `json:\\\"priority,omitempty\\\"`\\n    Author    string    `json:\\\"author,omitempty\\\"`\\n    Reviewers []Reviewer `json:\\\"reviewers,omitempty\\\"`\\n    CreatedAt time.Time `json:\\\"created_at\\\"`\\n    UpdatedAt time.Time `json:\\\"updated_at\\\"`\\n\\n    // REMOVED: Branch, Base (moved into BranchEntry)\\n    // NEW:\\n    Branches  []BranchEntry `json:\\\"branches\\\"`\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### BranchEntry (new)\\n\\n```go\\ntype BranchEntry struct {\\n    ID         string    `json:\\\"id\\\"`           // stable UUID\\n    Name       string    `json:\\\"name\\\"`         // branch name (informational, may go stale)\\n    BaseBranch string    `json:\\\"base_branch\\\"`  // target branch name (e.g., \\\"main\\\")\\n    BaseCommit string    `json:\\\"base_commit\\\"`  // fork point SHA (updated on rebase)\\n    PR         *PRRef    `json:\\\"pr,omitempty\\\"` // optional, replaceable\\n    AddedAt    time.Time `json:\\\"added_at\\\"`\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### PRRef (new)\\n\\n```go\\ntype PRRef struct {\\n    Number int    `json:\\\"number\\\"`\\n    URL    string `json:\\\"url,omitempty\\\"`\\n    Status string `json:\\\"status,omitempty\\\"` // open, merged, closed\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### Checkpoints stay per-trail, gain a BranchID field\\n\\n```go\\ntype CheckpointRef struct {\\n    CheckpointID string    `json:\\\"checkpoint_id\\\"`\\n    CommitSHA    string    `json:\\\"commit_sha\\\"`\\n    Summary      string    `json:\\\"summary,omitempty\\\"`\\n    CreatedAt    time.Time `json:\\\"created_at\\\"`\\n    // NEW:\\n    BranchID     string    `json:\\\"branch_id,omitempty\\\"` // links to BranchEntry.ID\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThis keeps `checkpoints.json` as a single flat file (easy to read the full trail history) while still allowing filtering by branch. The `BranchID` is optional for backward compat — existing checkpoints without it are assumed to belong to the first/only branch.\\n\\n---\\n\\nDoes this data model look right before I move to the next section?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":331,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":47448,\"output_tokens\":831,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":331,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYnkJvKE3oxBptxue3geh\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"bba35d1c-7b99-4331-ad55-0b280a65262e\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-07T00:09:07.510Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"bba35d1c-7b99-4331-ad55-0b280a65262e\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/1\",\"sessionId\":\"cc5ed6bd-0c2c-4c91-94f7-7c18e3bda941\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"alex/trails-multi-pr\",\"slug\":\"jazzy-inventing-fern\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.