xisting)\\n\\n#### Trail.go Types\\n\\n**ID (12-char hex, same as checkpoint ID):**\\n```go\\ntype ID string\\nfunc (id ID) Path() string { return string(id[:2]) + \\\"/\\\" + string(id[2:]) }\\nfunc (id ID) ShardParts() (shard, suffix string)\\n```\\n\\n**Metadata structure:**\\n```go\\ntype Metadata struct {\\n\\tTrailID   ID         `json:\\\"trail_id\\\"`\\n\\tBranch    string     `json:\\\"branch\\\"`        // Current branch name\\n\\tBase      string     `json:\\\"base\\\"`\\n\\tTitle     string     `json:\\\"title\\\"`\\n\\tBody      string     `json:\\\"body\\\"`\\n\\tStatus    Status     `json:\\\"status\\\"`        // draft, open, in_progress, in_review, merged, closed\\n\\tAuthor    string     `json:\\\"author\\\"`\\n\\tAssignees []string   `json:\\\"assignees\\\"`\\n\\tLabels    []string   `json:\\\"labels\\\"`\\n\\tCreatedAt time.Time  `json:\\\"created_at\\\"`\\n\\tUpdatedAt time.Time  `json:\\\"updated_at\\\"`\\n\\tMergedAt  *time.Time `json:\\\"merged_at\\\"`\\n\\tPriority  Priority   `json:\\\"priority,omitempty\\\"`\\n\\tType      Type       `json:\\\"type,omitempty\\\"`\\n\\tReviewers []Reviewer `json:\\\"reviewers,omitempty\\\"`\\n}\\n\\ntype CheckpointRef struct {\\n\\tCheckpointID string    `json:\\\"checkpoint_id\\\"`\\n\\tCommitSHA    string    `json:\\\"commit_sha\\\"`\\n\\tCreatedAt    time.Time `json:\\\"created_at\\\"`\\n\\tSummary      *string   `json:\\\"summary\\\"`\\n}\\n\\ntype Checkpoints struct {\\n\\tCheckpoints []CheckpointRef `json:\\\"checkpoints\\\"`\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 6. KEY PATTERNS FOR MULTI-BRANCH IMPLEMENTATION\\n\\n#### Reference Resolution Pattern\\n**Current:** Single trail per branch via `FindByBranch(branchName)`\\n**For multi-PR:** Need to\\n- Store multiple branch entries per trail (BranchEntry with stable UUID)\\n- Resolve active trail from current branch → find matching BranchEntry in trail → use TrailID\\n- Update trail's BranchEntries array instead of replacing single branch field\\n\\n#### Checkpoint